      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2025-04-08T20:14:13.227Z",
      "cooked": "<p>You can change your chain ring what is your biggest ring in the back? Or smallest in the front?   Probably the maximum you will achieve is 8\u2019 @ 120% very unlikely you get past that.  See below.  The only solution to get beyond 6-8 minutes is increase your FTP so you are only doing 110% of FTP, or what ever you need depending how many minutes it is.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b_2_690x335.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"pQ2YiveM9lMGB24yOEEJmHoBXPZ\" width=\"690\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b_2_690x335.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b_2_1035x502.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b5188718dc3405e0a65b62f13fa642ef5114f77b_2_1380x670.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"D3D6E2\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2542\u00d71236 259 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
