      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/blacktek/{size}/11188_2.png",
      "created_at": "2025-04-09T07:33:24.012Z",
      "cooked": "<p>tnx <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alex\">@Alex</a><br>\nthat segment was one that I ride in about 18 minutes (climb with 10% average slope + a final very steep part).</p>\n<p>I know about the stress on tendons and ligaments, but tnx for reminding me about them.</p>\n<p>Now let\u2019s see to increase FTP in the coming months/years <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>ps I try to have fun as first goal, but also try to not get down from saddle in the middle of slopes <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
